title: 820-3115 not recognizing battery
message: G3Hi s 12.22v, it stays on connected to a battery but doesnt see/recognize the battery. where to start?

title: 820-3115 not recognizing battery
message: Remove BIL and test again, are you testing with a known good battery?? Voltage on PPBUS_G3H is with only charger?? Diode mode measurements on pins 10 and 11 from U7000??

title: 820-3115 not recognizing battery
message: Without BIL the same results, new original battery, G3H is with only charger, diode mode 10 and 11 is 0.8
